---
// Real testimonials data extracted from the original HTML
---

<section id="testimonios" class="py-20 sm:py-24 md:py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div 
            class="text-center mb-14 sm:mb-16 md:mb-20"
            data-animate="fade-up"
        >
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 text-blue-600 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium tracking-wide uppercase mb-5">
                Testimonios
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-5">
                Opiniones <span class="text-gradient">reales</span> de personas reales
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Esto opinan las personas con las que hemos trabajado
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bento Grid Layout -->
        <div 
            class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 auto-rows-auto gap-5 sm:gap-6"
            data-animate-stagger
        >
            <!-- Card 1: Iván Fernández - Large featured quote -->
            <div 
                class="sm:col-span-2 group"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="h-full bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <!-- Subtle gradient -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50/30 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <!-- Quote icon -->
                        <svg class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 text-blue-100 mb-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
                        </svg>
                        
                        <!-- Quote text -->
                        <blockquote class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-slate-800 leading-snug mb-8" style="line-height: 1.35;">
                            "Es un tema de eficiencia. Es verdaderamente increíble que se pueda contactar un cliente potencial en menos de <span class="text-blue-500">20 segundos</span>."
                        </blockquote>
                        
                        <!-- Author info -->
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-5">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <img 
                                    src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild3339-6136-4063-b162-636231306139/12.png" 
                                    alt="Iván Fernández" 
                                    class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-slate-100"
                                    loading="lazy"
                                />
                                <div>
                                    <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-base sm:text-lg">Iván Fernández</div>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">CEO en Grupo Dental Clinics</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <img 
                                src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild3264-6664-4663-b830-336565336630/13.png" 
                                alt="Grupo Dental Clinics" 
                                class="h-14 sm:h-16 w-auto grayscale opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300 hidden sm:block"
                                loading="lazy"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2: Óscar Narváez -->
            <div 
                class="group"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="h-full bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all duration-500">
                    <blockquote class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium text-slate-800 leading-relaxed mb-6" style="line-height: 1.5;">
                        "Enviar recordatorios automatizados ha sido un <span class="text-blue-500">antes y después</span> en la clínica."
                    </blockquote>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <img 
                            src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild3738-6239-4664-b565-633862356339/10.png" 
                            alt="Óscar Narváez" 
                            class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-slate-100"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm sm:text-base">Óscar Narváez</div>
                            <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-500">Doctor Óscar Narváez</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3: Video testimonial -->
            <div 
                class="group"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="h-full bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-0 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden relative min-h-[220px] sm:min-h-[260px]">
                    <!-- Video embed -->
                    <iframe 
                        src="https://kinescope.io/embed/hWtq9FcmE27QNEMNWooojr?muted=true&autoplay=true&autopause=false&loop=true" 
                        allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; encrypted-media;"
                        frameborder="0"
                        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
                        loading="lazy"
                        title="Testimonio Grupo Dental Clinics"
                    ></iframe>
                    
                    <!-- Top overlay -->
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 p-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900/70 to-transparent z-10">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <img 
                                src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild3936-3762-4365-b032-623134626531/den.png" 
                                alt="Grupo Dental Clinics" 
                                class="h-5 sm:h-6 w-auto"
                                loading="lazy"
                            />
                            <span class="text-xs text-white/80">Clínica dental líder en el país</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Bottom caption -->
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900 to-transparent z-10">
                        <div class="text-sm sm:text-base font-bold text-white">"+80 pacientes nuevos gracias a la IA"</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 4: Stats - +450 reseñas -->
            <div 
                class="group"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="h-full bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-green-200 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden min-h-[180px]">
                    <!-- Subtle pattern -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
                        <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                            <defs>
                                <pattern id="grid-green" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                                    <path d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                                </pattern>
                            </defs>
                            <rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(#grid-green)" class="text-green-500"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-center">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                            <img 
                                src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild3837-3066-4138-a234-643430623136/sta.png" 
                                alt="5 estrellas" 
                                class="h-12 sm:h-14 w-auto"
                                loading="lazy"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gradient mb-1">+450</div>
                        <div class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 font-medium">reseñas positivas</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2">Tras mejorar la experiencia del paciente</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 5: Johanna Escobar -->
            <div 
                class="group"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="h-full bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all duration-500">
                    <blockquote class="text-base sm:text-lg font-medium text-slate-800 leading-relaxed mb-6" style="line-height: 1.55;">
                        "Si queríamos seguir siendo competitivos teníamos que <span class="text-blue-500">implementar la IA</span> cuanto antes."
                    </blockquote>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <img 
                            src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild6264-6538-4337-a264-353364346338/9.png" 
                            alt="Johanna Escobar" 
                            class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-11 sm:h-11 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-slate-100"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Johanna Escobar</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Marketing Clínicas Esquivel</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 6: Enrique Salmerón -->
            <div 
                class="group"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="h-full bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-violet-200 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-50/30 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <blockquote class="text-base sm:text-lg font-medium text-slate-800 leading-relaxed mb-6" style="line-height: 1.55;">
                            "No me imaginaba poder contactar a todos mis clientes las <span class="text-violet-500">24 horas del día</span>."
                        </blockquote>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <img 
                                src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild6338-3362-4335-b663-393837623133/11.png" 
                                alt="Enrique Salmerón" 
                                class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-11 sm:h-11 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-slate-100"
                                loading="lazy"
                            />
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Enrique Salmerón</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Doctor en ICPM</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 7: Alba Ortega - Large featured -->
            <div 
                class="sm:col-span-2 group"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="h-full bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-green-200 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50/30 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <!-- Quote icon -->
                        <svg class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 text-green-100 mb-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
                        </svg>
                        
                        <blockquote class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-slate-800 leading-snug mb-8" style="line-height: 1.35;">
                            "Antes no podíamos contactar a todos los leads, ahora lanzamos <span class="text-green-500">campañas personalizadas cada semana</span> de manera automatizada."
                        </blockquote>
                        
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-5">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <img 
                                    src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild6432-3935-4130-a434-646330376464/new.png" 
                                    alt="Alba Ortega" 
                                    class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-slate-100"
                                    loading="lazy"
                                />
                                <div>
                                    <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-base sm:text-lg">Alba Ortega</div>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">CM en Perfect Smile</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <img 
                                src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild6139-3836-4762-a133-663064313139/7.png" 
                                alt="Perfect Smile" 
                                class="h-14 sm:h-16 w-auto grayscale opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300 hidden sm:block"
                                loading="lazy"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 8: Stats - Agente 24/7 -->
            <div 
                class="group"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="h-full bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50/30 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
                            <img 
                                src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild6664-3537-4032-a265-353533396136/6.png" 
                                alt="Automatización" 
                                class="h-10 sm:h-12 w-auto grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300"
                                loading="lazy"
                            />
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Agente 24/7</div>
                        <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gradient mb-2">+213%</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Aumento en productividad</div>
                        
                        <div class="mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-slate-100">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <img 
                                    src="https://static.tildacdn.net/tild3666-3865-4139-a337-373633383237/3.png" 
                                    alt="Citas" 
                                    class="h-8 sm:h-10 w-auto grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300"
                                    loading="lazy"
                                />
                                <div>
                                    <div class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-500">+18%</div>
                                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Incremento en citas</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
